tables.table_schema:
CREATE TABLE users (
    user_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
    user_name VARCHAR(50),
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10),
    location VARCHAR(100),
    ethical_score FLOAT
)

CREATE TABLE users (
    user_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    username VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    age INT,
    gender VARCHAR(10)
);

CREATE TABLE users (
    user_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    username TEXT NOT NULL,
    email TEXT NOT NULL,
    age INT,
    gender TEXT,
    ethical_score INT
);

CREATE TABLE decisions (
    decision_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id INT REFERENCES users(user_id),
    decision TEXT NOT NULL,
    date TIMESTAMP,
    approval BOOLEAN
);

CREATE TABLE models (
    model_id SERIAL PRIMARY KEY,
    model_name TEXT NOT NULL,
    description TEXT,
    accuracy FLOAT,
    trained_date DATE
);

CREATE TABLE users (
    user_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    username VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    email VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    age INT,
    location VARCHAR(50)
);

CREATE TABLE user_preferences (
    preference_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    user_id UUID NOT NULL,
    privacy_level INT,
    ethical_threshold DECIMAL(5,2),
    training_data_path VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL
);

CREATE TABLE ai_models (
    model_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    model_name VARCHAR(50) NOT NULL,
    model_description TEXT,
    created_at TIMESTAMP,
    user_id UUID
);

CREATE TABLE model_training_data (
    data_id UUID PRIMARY KEY,
    model_id UUID NOT NULL,
    data_path VARCHAR(100) NOT NULL,
    data_size INT,
    uploaded_at TIMESTAMP
);

CREATE TABLE user_decisions (
  decision_id INT PRIMARY KEY,
  user_id INT REFERENCES users(user_id),
  model_id INT REFERENCES ethical_models(model_id),
  decision_text TEXT,
  decision_result VARCHAR(20)
);
